  <brief_title>Hydrogen Sulfide Detoxification and Butyrate Metabolism in Ulcerative Colitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact of the Mucosal Detoxification Mechanism of Hydrogen Sulphide on the Oxidation Pathway of Butyrate in Ulcerative Colitis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
