  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the relation between sulphide detoxification and
      butyrate metabolism at the level of gene expression and enzyme activity in ulcerative colitis
      patients and healthy controls.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
